# Project Overview

This is a Next.js application integrated with Clerk for authentication and Supabase for database functionality.

## Key Files

- [src/middleware.ts](mdc:src/middleware.ts) - Clerk middleware for authentication
- [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) - Root layout with Clerk provider and auth UI components
- [src/app/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/page.tsx) - Main page component

## Project Structure

- `/src` - Main source code
  - `/app` - Next.js App Router components
  - `middleware.ts` - Clerk authentication middleware
- `/public` - Static files

## Tech Stack

- Next.js 15 with App Router
- Clerk for authentication
- Supabase for database and backend services
- React 19
- TypeScript
